Kuthiwa amaphoyisa athola ulwazi ngesigameko sokubulala esasenzeke ngeSonto lapho kusakazwa khona izindaba zezigameko zobugebengu ezenzekile ngaphakathi emaphoyiseni. Ngaleso sikhathi kuthiwa umsolwa kulesi sigameko wayehamba ngezinyawo eyodlula esiteshini esingumahamba nendlawane esikwa-U. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Ntaal, uLt Col Thulani Zwane, uthe uphiko lwamaphoyisa ezinja lwelamele umsolwa esehamba nabanye abathathu. Laba basolwa bathe uma bebona amaphoyisa baqala badubula. Abathathu uthe babaleka becasha ngezindlu, oyedwa oneminyaka ewu-48 obekunguyena obefuneka wadubuleka emlenzeni ngesikhathi amaphoyisa edudulana ngenganono nabasolwa. “Lo msolwa kuthe uma eseshwa kwatholakala i-9mm Norinco nezinhlamvu kuye. Umsolwa uholele amaphoyisa komunye umuzi okwa-Q lapho kutholakale khona ezinye izibhamu ezincane nezinkulu kanye nezinhlamvu. Kuyo le ndlu kubuye kwaboshwa nomunye umsolwa oneminyaka ewu-58 otholakale nesibhamu nezinhlamvu ezingekho emthethweni,” kusho uLt Zwane. Bobabili abasolwa uthe bavele eNkantolo yeMantshi yakule ndawo ngamacala ababekwe wona ngoLwesibili.